!! Gantt Widget

The `gantt` widget is to render a gantt chart.

!! Syntax

```
<$gantt filter="[tag[Event]]" />
```


!! Content and attributes
|!Attributes |!Type |!Description |
|filter |required|The `filter` to select events |
|start |optional|The `start` field for event start. If missing, the `start` field will be used |
|end |optional|The `end` field for event end. If missing, the `end` field will be used |

!! Example

```
<$gantt filter="[tag[Event]]"/>
```

<$gantt filter="[tag[Event]]"/>
